Inter Milan Says Gian Piero Gasperini Will Be Soccer Club’s New Manager

-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n
-- 
2011-06-24T14:18:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-24/inter-milan-says-gian-piero-gasperini-will-be-soccer-club-s-new-manager.html
Inter Milan FC said Gian Piero
Gasperini, the former trainer of Genoa, will be the team’s new
coach. Gasperini, 53, will sign a two-year contract, according
to Inter’s website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
